                    <h2 class="post-title">The Rise of Artificial Intelligence</h2>
                    <p class="post-meta">February 03, 2024 by Daniel</p>
                    <p class="post-content">Artificial Intelligence (AI) is reshaping industries and transforming our world. From autonomous vehicles to advanced healthcare systems, AI is revolutionizing the way we live and work.</p>
                </div> -->
                <!-- Blog post 2 -->
                <!-- <div class="blog-post">
                    <h2 class="post-title">Exploring the Potential of Machine Learning</h2>
                    <p class="post-meta">February 03, 2024 by Dani</p>
                    <p class="post-content">Machine Learning (ML) algorithms are unlocking new possibilities in areas such as predictive analytics, natural language processing, and computer vision. Let's delve into the exciting world of ML and its applications.</p>
                </div> -->
                <!-- Add more blog posts here -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and jQuery CDN -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>